CNCP v1 22543
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7156: Use the parent directory name as the component name",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:26.911763+00:00",
  "text": "Use the parent directory name as the component name\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\n\ncomponentName(\"/order/Index.vue\")=\"Order\"\n\n### What does the proposed API look like?\n\n1. 检查所有用到正则`/([^/\\\\]+)\\.\\w+$/`的代码\r\n2. （正确）获取componentName的部分代码\r\n```\r\nconst match = Component.__file.match(/([/\\\\](\\w+))?([/\\\\](\\w+))\\.\\w+$/)\r\nif (match) {\r\n    if (capitalize(match[4]) === \"Index\") {\r\n        const dirName = match[2]\r\n        name = capitalize(dirName)\r\n    } else {\r\n        name = match[4]\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request"
  ],
